    "**4. Factorial Using Recursion**\n",
    "\n",
    "Problem Statement: Write a Python program to get the factorial of a non-negative integer using recursion.\n",
    "\n",
    "\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "id": "003e7355",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "5040\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "def factorial (n):\n",
    "    if n <=1:\n",
    "        return 1\n",
    "    else:\n",
    "        return n * factorial (n-1)\n",
    "\n",
    "print (factorial (7))"
   ]
  }
